data.description: Step inside this 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home that has everything you will need. Quaint kitchen and large enclosed outdoor patio for those warm summer days. With amenities such as pool, organic garden, community dining area, gym facilities, exercise classes, hair salon, organized activities and much more. Close to the dog park and picturesque hiking and walking trails. Located a short drive to restaurants, golf, shopping, the beach and all the Monterey Peninsula has to offer. Come and see why Hacienda Carmel with its well-equipped 55+ community is what you have been looking for.
